ttp_template:
<group name="bandwidth">
   Bandwidth {{BANDWIDTH | ORPHRASE}} kbps
</group>
<group name="queue_limit">
   Queue-limit {{QUEUE_LIMIT | ORPHRASE}}
</group>
cli_content:
Policy: MyQoS
 Class Map: HighPriority
  Match: dscp 46 (ef)
  Actions: 
   Priority level 1
   Bandwidth 10000 kbps
   Queue-limit 200 ms

 Class Map: MediumPriority
  Match: dscp 26
  Actions: 
   Bandwidth 2000 kbps
   Queue-limit 400 ms

 Class Map: LowPriority
  Match: dscp 20
  Actions: 
   Bandwidth 500 kbps
   Queue-limit 800 ms

Policy: AnotherQoS
 Class Map: HighPriority
  Match: dscp 34
  Actions: 
   Priority level 2
   Bandwidth 15000 kbps
   Queue-limit 100 ms

 Class Map: DefaultClass
  Match: any
  Actions: 
   Bandwidth 1000 kbps
   Queue-limit 1000 ms
textfsm_template:
Value POLICY (\S+)
Value CLASS_MAP (\S+)
Value MATCH (dscp \d+|any)
Value PRIORITY_LEVEL (\d+)
Value BANDWIDTH (\d+)
Value QUEUE_LIMIT (\d+ ms)

Start
  ^Policy: ${POLICY}$$
  ^\s*Class Map: ${CLASS_MAP}$$
  ^\s*Match: ${MATCH}$$
  ^\s*Actions:$$
  ^\s*Priority level ${PRIORITY_LEVEL}$$
  ^\s*Bandwidth ${BANDWIDTH} kbps$$
  ^\s*Queue-limit ${QUEUE_LIMIT}$$ -> Record
